PLAYER HELP
ACCEPT
Accept an offer. Typically you will use this when people try to ~CCOMgive~CHLP things to you, and when making 
deals using the ~CCOMtrade~CHLP system. For example:

 ~CDEFBob offers to give you: ~CCOMa warhammer~CDEF.
 ~CDEFType ~CCOMaccept~CDEF or ~CCOMreject~CDEF.
 > ~CCOMaccept
 ~CACTBob gives a warhammer to you.~CHLP

If a player is on your trusted list, you will automatically accept any offers from them.

~CCOMSee also: ~CREFautotake, give, trust, reject
